    "body": "Not an easy topic indeed, this is also the current behavior in instantsearch.js V1 (the one that is surprising).\r\n\r\nI have no silver bullet for this and what you propose @redox can be disturbing as well I guess since the changes in pagination UI are very small (page change) compared to the fact that the whole page is gonna be updated after scrolling top.\r\n\r\nWhat could work is a very fast/nice fadein fadeout effect. And having the API semantics to be able to trigger that. ",
